Title: Welcome to camp
Descriptions: Heh, I see you made it to camp. If you will be helpful you will be welcome. If not.. well.. then we will have zombie bait. It's simple really... **smiles** so you want to be helpful? Then go to Stary Sobor, the zombies are getting thick up there. Lets see how helpful you can be. Thin em out.
Kill a bunch of zombies around Stary Sobor to make things a little safer at camp
ObjectiveText: Kill a bunch of zombies around Stary Sobor to make things a little safer at camp
